{"tid":165700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本週三被告家屬暫緩籌款事宜，以免影響日後法律程序。","createTime":"2017-03-21T14:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T14:24:35.000Z","uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9fc2f6f38f65219d8e84c049b663321aec076ed9","tid":165700,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"早前敝司為本週三被告家屬籌款，惟反應熱烈，出乎被告家人意料，對家人造成不便；被告律師亦建議被告家屬判決後從長計議，暫緩籌款事宜，以免影響日後法律程序。故此，敝司現暫停為週三被告籌款，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n本土創作室之名信片仍然會繼續售賣，收益扣除成本之後將全數用作支援本土義士。<br />\n<br />\n本土新聞社長 Joel Lau 謹啟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localpresshk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalpresshk%2F&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=353eeffb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localpresshk/</a><br />\n<br />\n梳，我唔識貼LINK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248a3eec09253c0f5759def02702d472f1b7a212","tid":165700,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T14:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}